title: TAROT - WITCH OF THE BLACK ROSE 081 (2013) (c2c) (3 covers) (TLK
description:
TAROT WITCH OF THE BLACK ROSE #81
(Mature Readers)

Publisher: BROADSWORD COMICS

(Writer/Artist/Cover Artist) Jim Balent

Raven Hex, The Skeleton Man, Thornwic, and the Witch Mother, having discovered the camp of the Dark Faeries, make plans to rescue the bewitched Tarot. But some plans require a sacrifice. A life for a life - and maybe more! The unseelie court sets its lethal gaze upon a new enemy.

In Shops: 7/31/2013
